import sys

n = int(sys.stdin.readline().strip())
a = [int(x) for x in sys.stdin.readline().strip().split()]

mex = 1
for i in range(n):
    if a[i] > mex:
        mex = a[i] + 1

n=int(input())

    if a[i] not in b:
        b.append(a[i])
    else:
        b.remove(a[i])
